00:43:11,761 --> 00:43:15,291
♫  In my memories, sweat dampened your face  ♫

711
00:43:15,291 --> 00:43:18,701
♫  Still shining just as brightly  ♫

712
00:43:18,701 --> 00:43:24,781
♫  Looking forward to the day  ♫ 
 ♫  When we meet again  ♫

